  "ai_usage": "Use as a ready-to-ship Podcast page. Copy the whole file; reskin by editing the :root custom properties (colors/radius/font) and replacing the content in each <section>. Sections are independent — reorder or delete freely. It composes catalog effects inline (animated gradient hero, glassmorphic sticky nav, scroll-triggered reveals, card hover-lift, a scroll-progress bar, and gradient text) so you get a premium feel with zero dependencies. Replace the gradient placeholder blocks with real <img> (add alt text). Responsive and reduced-motion safe out of the box.",
